Brix laughs at Ramulus' remark, but Gekkidama interupts.

"Laughing? LAUGHING! There's nothing to laugh about here. You're 
about to die. Let's go!"

Gekkidama charges with grenade launchers armed. He bypasses Ramulus 
and jumps right on top of Brix. They wrestle on the ground for 
awhile, going back and forth, until finaly Gekkidama put his launcher 
up against Brix' head.

"Looks like you've lost your edge Captain....or maybe my insanity has 
given new strength. Doesn't matter. Bye-bye Brix."

"Ramulus! Get him off me!"
